These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, papaya, tomato, eggplant
1. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
3. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | lime | papaya | tomato | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, cola, tea
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk | tea | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, dancing, collecting, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | collecting | dancing | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, western, romance, action
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | horror | action | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, baseball, tennis, parkour
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | parkour | tennis | baseball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
