3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | family | martial-arts | spy |

