.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, lemon, kiwi, grapes
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the person eating onion and the person eating grapes##2
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
4. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | grapes | lemon | onion | kiwi |

