1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | lizard | cat | fish | guinea-pig |

