.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-19::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, snake, dog
1. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
4. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2     |    3    |  4   |
| Pet   | snake | rat | hedgehog | dog |

