.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, ambient, dubstep
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | trance | hip-hop | dubstep |

 